msgstr "ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:16
msgid "Contiguous Selection Tool"
msgstr "連続領域選択ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:18
msgid "|toolselectcontiguous|"
msgstr "|toolselectcontiguous|"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:20
msgid ""
"This tool, represented by a magic wand, allows you to make :ref:`selections_basics` by selecting a point of color. It will select any contiguous areas of a similar color to the one you selected. You"
" can adjust the \"fuzziness\" of the tool in the tool options dock. A lower number will select colors closer to the color that you chose in the first place."
msgstr "魔法の杖で表示されるこのツールは、色を選択することで\\ :ref:`selections_basics`\\ を作成できます。選択したものと似た色が続く連続したエリアを選択します。ツールのオプションドッカーから\"あいまいさ\"を調整できます。低い数字にすれば最初に選択した色により近い色を選択するようになります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:23
msgid "Hotkeys and Sticky keys"
msgstr "ホットキーとスティッキーキー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:25
msgid ":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'add'. You can release the :kbd:`Shift` key while dragging, but it will still be set to 'add'. Same for the others."
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| で次の選択を'追加'します。ドラッグしながら :kbd:`Shift` キーを離しても'追加'に設定されたままになります。他も同様です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:26
msgid ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'subtract'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| で次される選択を'除外'します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:27
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'replace'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| で次される選択に'置換'します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:28
msgid ":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'intersect'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| で次される選択との'積集合'を取ります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:32
msgid "Hovering over a selection allows you to move it."
msgstr "選択の上にマウスホバーすることで動かすことができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:33
msgid "|mouseright| will open up a selection quick menu with amongst others the ability to edit the selection."
msgstr "|mouseright| で選択を編集できる選択クイックメニューが開きます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:37
msgid "You can switch the behavior of the :kbd:`Alt` key to use the :kbd:`Ctrl` key instead by toggling the switch in the :ref:`general_settings`."
msgstr ":ref:`general_settings` から :kbd:`Alt` キーと :kbd:`Ctrl` キーのふるまいを入れ替えることができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:40
msgid "Tool Options"
msgstr "ツールのオプション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:44
msgid "Threshold"
msgstr "しきい値"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:44
msgid "This controls whether or not the contiguous selection sees another color as a border."
msgstr "どこまで他の色を選択の境界としてみるかを操作できます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:49
msgid "Spread"
msgstr "拡張"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:49
msgid "Set how far the fully opaque portion of the selection should extend. See :ref:`fill_tool` for extra explanation."
msgstr "選択範囲の不透明部分をどこまで拡張するかを設定します。詳細は\\ :ref:`fill_tool`\\ を参照してください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:54
msgid "This option sets the minimum gap size that the contiguous fill will be able to propagate into."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:58
msgid ""
"Left: The original image (black over white) and a green dot marking where the contiguous selection will be initiated. Center: The selection marquee after a selection operation using a gap size of 0 "
"pixels. Right: The selection marquee after a selection operation using a gap size of 8 pixels. Note that the selected regions are emphasized with a light pink color for clarity sake."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:59
msgid "Selection Extent"
msgstr "選択の拡張"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:59
msgid "Close Gap"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:62
msgid "Anti-alias"
msgstr "アンチエイリアス"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:63
msgid ""
"This will smooth the jagged edges present in the selection. It differs from feathering in that this will smooth in the direction of the edge instead of all directions, and only if the edge is jagged"
" (high contrast)."
msgstr "選択のギザギザを滑らかにします。これはぼかしとは異なります。ぼかしはすべての方向に滑らかにしますが、アンチエイリアスは境界の方向にのみ滑らかにします。また、境界がギザギザである場合のみ滑らかにします。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:64
msgid "Grow Selection"
msgstr "拡大"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:65
msgid "This value extends (positive values) or contracts (negative values) the selection."
msgstr "この値で選択範囲を拡張(正の値)または縮小(負の値)します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:67
msgid "Adjustments"
msgstr "補正"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:67
msgid "Feathering Radius"
msgstr "塗り広げ"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/contiguous_select.rst:67
msgid "This value will add a soft border to the selection."
msgstr "選択形状の境界に柔らかさを追加します。"

